00:00:11.640 --> 00:00:17.080
a clinic primarily for folks with opioid use disorder. We have multiple

00:00:17.080 --> 00:00:22.240
doctors on our team, medical providers, we also have some nurse practitioners

00:00:22.540 --> 00:00:27.600
and they all do opioid agonist therapy prescribing, or some people call

00:00:27.600 --> 00:00:30.800
OAT or O R T, Opioid Replacement Therapy.

