We serve people who are living in the modular housing buildings,

00:01:31.860 --> 00:01:37.380
the temporary modulars, the emergency response center shelter, the Salvation

00:01:37.380 --> 00:01:43.940
Army, shelter Richmond House and people who are also working full time and

