have a past history of opioid use disorder. But from what I'm gathering

00:01:48.820 --> 00:01:52.260
from speaking with clients at the clinic and as I get to know

00:01:52.260 --> 00:01:56.280
everybody, they feel really welcomed to come into the clinic.

