and anti stigma work, what else can we do to make this a

00:02:11.980 --> 00:02:18.760
more welcoming, decolonizing, less institutional place where people feel

00:02:18.760 --> 00:02:23.260
comfortable coming in and getting their needs met and getting services that

00:02:23.260 --> 00:02:30.040
they require. We don't want to be punishing

